# Game Dev Tycoon — Project Overview

Browser-based idle/incremental game where you run a game development studio. Built with Next.js 15 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript, ShadCN/UI, Tailwind CSS v4, and Zustand.

## Directory Layout

```
src/
  app/              — Next.js pages (/ = main menu, /game = gameplay)
  components/
    ui/             — ShadCN primitives (do not edit directly)
    screens/        — Full-screen components (MainMenu, BankruptcyScreen)
    game/           — Gameplay UI (StudioHeader, MonthEndModal, tabs/)
      tabs/         — One component per game tab
  lib/
    config/         — ALL tunable constants, flags, and balance numbers
    game/           — Pure game logic (no React, no side effects)
    store/          — Zustand store and save/load serialization
```

## Key Principles

- **Config-driven**: Every magic number lives in `src/lib/config/`. Never hardcode balance values in components or game logic.
- **Pure game logic**: Files in `src/lib/game/` are pure functions with no React imports. They take state in, return new state out.
- **Zustand store**: Single store in `src/lib/store/gameStore.ts`. Components read via selectors. Mutations happen through store actions only.
- **ShadCN components**: Treat `src/components/ui/` as a library — import from it, don't modify it.
